        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">foo</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kt\">Sort</span> <span class=\"mi\">33</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>maximum universe level offset threshold (32) has been reached, you can increase the limit using option <code>set_option maxUniverseOffset &lt;limit&gt;</code>, but you are probably misusing universe levels since offsets are usually small natural numbers</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>I feel like I've been told off <span aria-label=\"oops\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f643\" role=\"img\" title=\"oops\">:oops:</span></p>",
